            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/unnamed_1.png?VersionId=bE.sdEAfhIX84saTZElMGA6QMWZ4UWNF&amp;itok=77LwwdO5" title="《联合早报》记者杨丹旭在中国新任总理李强的首次总理记者会上提问。（视频截图）" alt="《联合早报》记者杨丹旭在中国新任总理李强的首次总理记者会上提问。（视频截图）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-03/unnamed_1.png?VersionId=bE.sdEAfhIX84saTZElMGA6QMWZ4UWNF&amp;itok=77LwwdO5" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
